  "title": "Better Drift Boats",
  "description": "The combination of the Better Boats and Drift Boats",
  "body": "<p align=\"center\">Every single boat withBetter Drift Boats combines the ideas of Better Boats and Drift Boats into a single resource pack that improves the overall shape and style of Minecraft boats.</p>\n<p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/50497a6f42a3faeabac37d0404b034ac1d443e74.png\" alt=\"Better Drift Boats Title\" width=\"900\"></p>\n<p align=\"center\">It adds a slight seating slope and curved front for a more natural design, along with drift-inspired details like spoilers, lights, and front and rear windshields.</p>\n<p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/b2a7e39a7694ee97d8c3d1c53bc55f530b48dccd.png\" alt=\"Horizontal Line\" width=\"1000\"></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/fef66261f263bdb287997e4745686e811895bf2c.png\" alt=\"Sample\" width=\"200\"></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/14ff3cefa563f8979b6168bea253a552fe07577d_0.webp\" alt=\"Boats Sample\" width=\"700\"></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/b2a7e39a7694ee97d8c3d1c53bc55f530b48dccd.png\" alt=\"Horizontal Line\" width=\"1000\"></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/663282aa64e38268989d34f909375e16a661f105.png\" alt=\"Requirements\" width=\"900\"></p>\n<p align=\"center\">This resource pack is made possible with an OptiFine feature called custom entity models (CEM) to add new entity models and animations.</p>\n<p align=\"center\">Entity Model Features and Entity Texture Features (EMF & ETF) can be used as an alternative to OptiFine.</p>\n<p align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/entity-model-features\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/9d4e0ebb27db7813bbcaa9d95f12e51ff2592f3c.png\" alt=\"EMF Download Button\" width=\"400\"></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/entitytexturefeatures\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/2dfa7a42c56ca17a16d31053fd77a453dde025cd.png\" alt=\"ETF Download Button\" width=\"400\"></a></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://optifine.net/downloads\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/4c14f141c0a4cf9cdedbd2aebc727f56b5a1914d.png\" alt=\"Optifine Downloads Button\" width=\"400\"></a></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/b2a7e39a7694ee97d8c3d1c53bc55f530b48dccd.png\" alt=\"Horizontal Line\" width=\"1000\"></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><img \nsrc=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/15b77794ebebe05b33cec6bf85dfa5c8c01eca05.png\" alt=\"Update\" width=\"200\"></p>\n<p align=\"center\">This update improves the accuracy and polish of the pack.</p>\n<p align=\"center\">Door edge textures (top, bottom, left, and right) now use proper textures instead of stretched pixels.</p>\n<details><summary>Update 1.1:</summary></details>\n<p align=\"center\">The pack icon has been updated and the resource pack \"Broken or incompatible\" warnings in Minecraft have been fixed.</p>\n<p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/b2a7e39a7694ee97d8c3d1c53bc55f530b48dccd.png\" alt=\"Horizontal Line\" width=\"1000\"></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/better-drift-boats\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/9d3cd7c29b765ea051a12413a8580e6b002c04ff.png\" alt=\"Modrinth Download Button\" width=\"300\"></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/members/patrickool/projects\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/425e2c3a8f7ca6ba05b2d4ea767640abc7b5ae71.png\" alt=\"CurseForge Download Button\" width=\"300\"></a></p>",
